data.description: New Generation Home in Tuscany Meadows, Home has a Unique Generational Suite, which is basically an apartment within the home. It has a separate, living room, kitchen area, with microwave, dishwasher, Island with granite top, pantry, refrigerator, laundry, walk in closet and a full bath, along with a separate entrance to separate walkway. This would be great for a mother in Law Plan or Older Child. In addition the home has 3 bedrooms and two full baths, two living areas and an office. In addition the gourmet kitchen has an abundance of dark custom cabinets, working center Island, breakfast bar, stainless appliances., Nice Patio overlooking the backyard and greenbelt.
